#
# ROOM LAYOUT:
#   Reception Lobby → Security Office (Patricia Morgan, mission handler)
#   Reception Lobby → Break Room → Main Office Area (Kevin Park IT admin)
#   Main Office Area → Research Lab (Dr. Chen, badge required)
